title: Matched
description: When a computer dating program matches Beast Boy to Raven, he tries wooing her to disastrous effect.

title: TV Knight 8
description: Commissioner Gordon has to work, so Batman joins him at the GCPD for fun and crimefighting.

title: Toilet Water
description: When the Titans dog-sit for Superman, Robin tries to keep the others from spoiling Krypto.

title: Plot Holes
description: After learning about movie plot holes, the Titans have some fun but end up throwing their world into chaos.

title: Beard Hunter
description: On a camping trip, The Chief shows off his beard, but warns the Doom Patrol about the Beard Hunter.

title: Second Christmas
description: The Titans trick Starfire into believing in second Christmas with second Santa.

title: The Great Holiday Escape
description: When they learn that Beast Boy sent Santa to jail, the Titans plan to infiltrate the prison to break him out.

title: TV Knight 2
description: Batman and Commissioner Gordon have a slumber party and watch their favorite TV shows.

title: Haunted Tank
description: At a Halloween festival, the Titans meet the famous Haunted Tank and its ghostly inhabitant, General Tucker.

title: Always Be Crimefighting
description: Looking to motivate them, Robin tells the Titans to solve some crimes or they're fired.

title: TV Knight 3
description: Batman is more interested in watching TV than participating in his birthday party.

title: Easter Annihilation
description: When Cyborg's egg hunt tech stops working, the Titans go to their satellite to find out what happened.

title: TV Knight
description: Batman and Commissioner Gordon check in on various happenings around Jump City.

title: Negative Feels
description: Negative Girls starts feeding on negative energy, so the Doom Patrol must stay positive before it's too late.

title: Books
description: Raven shows the rest of the Titans that books can be fun.

title: Intro
description: Control Freak leads the Titans on a chase through various cartoon intro sequences.

title: Christmas Magic
description: After the Titans get shrunken by Mumbo's magic, they must scale a Christmas Tree to prevent Mumbo from ruining their Christmas.

title: Colors of Raven
description: A magical prism causes Raven to fragment into five distinct personalities which wreak havoc around town until the other Titans can figure out how to rejoin her.

title: Utility Belt
description: Worried that he's only special because of his utility belt, Robin donates it to a thrift store.

title: Looking For Love
description: When they receive an alert that Love is missing, the Titans set out to find her using musical clues.

title: Lazy Sunday
description: When the Titans replace the couch with a treadmill, Cyborg and Beast Boy must get guidance from the couch spirit.

title: The Left Leg
description: When the gang bands together to form a giant robot, Robin is relegated to the left leg - but he makes the left leg count!

title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

title: Elasti-Bot
description: After ElastGirl is pushed to her limit, The Chief builds a robot replacement.

title: A Stickier Situation
description: When Sticky Joe tries to clip his pet rat's nails, it leads to a wild adventure.

title: New Chum
description: To prove he is extreme, Robotman becomes friends with King Shark and his gang of suckerfish.

title: Halloween vs. Christmas
description: When Santa tries to take over Halloween, it's up to the Titans and a few ghouls to stop him.

title: Our House
description: Trying to get the Doom Patrol's house condemned, The Brain becomes a home inspector.

title: Arthur
description: Robin threatens to fire Dr. Light unless he starts coming up with more inventive schemes.

title: Wishbone
description: The Titans make wishes on a wishbone, but when it's broken, they must travel to Gobble-Gobble Land to set things right.

title: Beast Boy on a Shelf
description: Santa Claus forces Beast Boy to become a spy and report on the Titans' naughty behavior.

title: Welcome To Halloween
description: Continuing their adventure with Pepo, the Titans escape the cold in a nearby castle, where they meet Krampus.

title: Teen Titans Action
description: In order to get a toy license deal with the Toy Master, the Titans become action heroes.

title: Warner Bros 100TH Anniversary
description: The Titans are in charge of the 100th Anniversary party for Warner Bros on the studio lot and everything is going well until the magical WB Shield is broken into pieces.

title: Winning a Golf Tournament Is the Solution to All of Life's Money Problems
description: After the T-Car is towed due to outstanding parking tickets, Robin has Cyborg enter a golf tournament for the cash prize.

title: The Brain of the Family
description: The Brain's home life is disrupted when his slacker brother Brian comes to visit. Now The Brain and Mallah have to deal with Brian's messes and keep him from ruining their big secret scheme.

title: The True Meaning of Christmas
description: Fed up with never getting presents from Santa, the Titans head to the north pole to take themselves off the Naughty List by any means necessary.
